trans-unit.source: Determines the serialization method used for a <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer serialisering metoden som brukes en <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings.SerializeAs%2A> property of the <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> object controls the serialization mode for a single profile property setting.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings.SerializeAs%2A>-egenskapen til det <xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings>objektet kontrollerer serialiseringsmodus for egenskapsinnstillingen enkelt profil.</xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings> </xref:System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings.SerializeAs%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"></xref> object is serialized using binary serialization.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"> </xref> objektet serialiseres med binær Serialiseringsfeil.

trans-unit.source: The provider has implicit knowledge of the type and is responsible for deciding how to serialize the <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"></xref> object into the data store.
trans-unit.target: Leverandøren har implisitt kunnskap om typen og er ansvarlig for å bestemme hvordan du serialisere den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"> </xref> objektet i datakilden.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"></xref> object is serialized to a simple string.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"> </xref> objektet er serialisert til en enkelt streng.

trans-unit.source: The profile <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"></xref> is serialized as XML using XML serialization.
trans-unit.target: Profilen <xref href="System.Web.Configuration.ProfilePropertySettings"> </xref> serialiseres som XML ved hjelp av XML-serialisering.
